# KnowledgeHub – AI-Powered Collaborative Notes (MERN + Gemini)

An AI-powered **collaborative knowledge hub** where teams can create, manage, and search documents.  
Built with **MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js** and **Google Gemini AI**.  

Features:
- Authentication – Email/Password + JWT (user/admin roles)
- Document Management– Create, edit, delete, summarize, tag
- AI Integration – Gemini for auto summaries, tags, semantic search, and Q&A
- Search – Regular text + semantic search
- Team Q&A – Ask AI questions using stored documents as context
- Modern UI – Built with React, Vite, Tailwind, and ShadCN

---

